summary: An ordinance accepting deeds and easements, for street and slope purposes, from Lizabeth J. Deyoe and others, to portions of the southwest one-quarter of the northwest one-quarter of the northwest one-quarter of the northwest one-quarter of Section 19, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W. M., and other properties, and laying off Evanston Avenue, Dayton Avenue, Phinney Avenue, Stone Avenue and North 141st Street.
